sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Gateway<br/>Platform Auth
    participant HTTP as Caikit HTTP Server<br/>8080/TCP
    participant gRPC as Caikit gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP
    participant Runtime as Caikit Runtime<br/>Module Router
    participant TGIS as TGIS Backend<br/>gRPC (configurable port)
    participant STModel as sentence-transformers<br/>Local Model
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Torch as Torch Distributed<br/>29550/TCP

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 1: HTTP Text Generation (Remote TGIS Backend)
    Client->>KServe: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Platform Auth
    KServe->>HTTP: Forward Request<br/>Configurable TLS
    HTTP->>Runtime: Route to TextGenerationTGIS Module
    Runtime->>TGIS: gRPC Generate Request<br/>Configurable mTLS
    TGIS-->>Runtime: Generated Text Response
    Runtime-->>HTTP: Generation Result
    HTTP-->>KServe: HTTP Response
    KServe-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: gRPC Text Generation (Remote TGIS Backend)
    Client->>gRPC: TextGenerationTaskService.Generate<br/>Configurable mTLS
    gRPC->>Runtime: Route to TextGenerationTGIS Module
    Runtime->>TGIS: gRPC Generate Request<br/>Configurable mTLS
    TGIS-->>Runtime: Generated Text Response
    Runtime-->>gRPC: gRPC Response
    gRPC-->>Client: Protobuf Response

    Note over Client,STModel: Flow 3: Local Text Embedding Inference
    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>Configurable TLS
    HTTP->>Runtime: Route to EmbeddingModule
    Runtime->>STModel: In-process Embedding<br/>sentence-transformers
    STModel-->>Runtime: Embedding Vectors
    Runtime-->>HTTP: Embedding Result
    HTTP-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Runtime,Torch: Flow 4: PEFT Prompt Tuning Training
    Note right of Runtime: Training Job triggers<br/>PeftPromptTuning.train()
    Runtime->>Runtime: Load HuggingFace Model<br/>via HFAutoCausalLM
    opt Model Download Enabled
        Runtime->>HFHub: Download Model Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, API Token
        HFHub-->>Runtime: Model Files
    end
    Runtime->>Runtime: PEFT Prompt Tuning<br/>Local PyTorch Training
    opt Multi-GPU Training
        Runtime->>Torch: torchrun Coordination<br/>29550/TCP, plaintext
    end
    Runtime-->>Runtime: Save Tuned Prompts
